|text1     = In Currency Wars, each character has their own {{Color|h|nobold=1|"Cost"}}, which is the number of Gold Coins required to recruit them.<br />The costs are {{Color|#b4b4|1-cost}}, {{Color|#6cce|2-cost}}, {{Color|#7196|3-cost}}, {{Color|#927f|4-cost}}, or {{Color|#ffd4|5-cost}}.
|image2    = Tutorial Character Cost 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_10000502.png>-<Tutorial Character Cost 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = Characters receive different levels of {{Color|h|nobold=1|initial boost}} to their combat abilities based on their cost.<br />Generally, {{Color|#ffd4|5-cost}} > {{Color|#927f|4-cost}} > {{Color|#7196|3-cost}} > {{Color|#6cce|2-cost}} > {{Color|#b4b4|1-cost}}, with characters of the same cost having {{Color|h|nobold=1|similar combat capabilities}}.
